register(uint32,uint8,uint256,(uint8,byt.details: Register parachain, along with index of Tellor pallet within corresponding runtime.

params._feeLocation: XcmTransactorV2.Multilocation The location of the currency type of consumer chain.
params._palletInstance: uint8 The index of the Tellor pallet within the parachain's runtime.
params._weightToFee: uint256 The constant multiplier(fee per weight) used to convert weight to fee
params._weights: Weights Weight of dispatchables on the corresponding pallet
